title: Trump slams Texas 'RINOS' over Paxton impeachment effort
description: The GOP-majority Texas House convened Saturday to begin impeachment proceedings against Attorney General Ken Paxton.

title: Texas’ GOP-held House set for impeachment proceedings against AG Ken Paxton
description: The House scheduled an afternoon start for debate on whether to impeach and suspend Paxton from office over allegations of bribery, unfitness for office and abuse of public trust.
